sub_title: Owner of English Explained || English Language Trainer || ADHD Coach
summary:
Hello! 
I am a creative person always moving around (literally and figuratively ;)). 
I started my own business as an English language tutor and ADHD coach: helping children in primary and secondary education, parents of children with ADHD, students and professionals with ADHD and/ or English language skills. 

All of my work in English is aimed at growing confident and becoming a professional fluent speaker, writer, listener and reader of English. I translate and proof-read documentation and have experience as a content creator and website designer/translator. 

My work as an ADHD coach revolves around support at school, studying and finding that all important work-life balance. This is all on top of helping you understand your distractible brain. 

See my website www.englishexplained.nl for more information or contact me directly at englishexplainedtrainings@gmail.com
